    Image image = ImageIO.read(url);
    this.setIconImage(image);
}
catch (IOException ex) {
    // Do what you want with caught exception.
    ex.printStackTrace();
}
```

Don&#39;t even bother with Examples #1 and #2, they now just remain here for reference. Just use either Example #3 or Example #4. Both will work in the IDE or a distributive JAR file.

